@page "/"

<div class="transparent-panel">
    <h1 class="rainbow-text">Welcome to Monster-Stop</h1>

    <p style="margin-top:20px; line-height:1.6;">
        Monster-Stop is your ultimate online store for the best energy drinks. We provide a wide selection 
        of beverages, from classic flavors to zero-sugar and special-edition varieties, all sourced 
        from top-notch suppliers.
    </p>

    <h2 style="margin-top:30px; color:#e1e1ff;">What You’ll Find Here</h2>
    <ul style="list-style:none; padding-left:0; margin-top:20px; line-height:1.8; color:#fff;">
        <li><strong>Product Management:</strong> Add, edit, and remove products using our admin panel.</li>
        <li><strong>Categories & Suppliers:</strong> Manage categories to keep products organized, and maintain a list of suppliers.</li>
        <li><strong>Order & OrderItems:</strong> Track orders placed by customers and the items within each order.</li>
        <li><strong>Filtering & Grouping:</strong> Easily filter products by category and view them grouped by supplier for better organization.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="margin-top:30px; color:#e1e1ff;">Key Features</h2>
    <p style="line-height:1.6;">
        Our project showcases a modern Blazor Server application integrated with EF Core for data management. 
        Enjoy futuristic styling with neon gradients, glassmorphic panels, and dynamic visual effects. We’ve 
        implemented full CRUD operations for multiple entities, user-friendly filtering, and a cohesive admin 
        interface.
    </p>

    <h2 style="margin-top:30px; color:#e1e1ff;">Navigation</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom:20px; line-height:1.6;">
        Use the top navigation bar to access different sections of the site:
    </p>

    <div style="display:flex; gap:20px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:30px;">
        <a href="/admin/products" class="btn-neon">Products Admin</a>
        <a href="/admin/categories" class="btn-neon">Categories Admin</a>
        <a href="/admin/suppliers" class="btn-neon">Suppliers Admin</a>
        <a href="/filterbycategory" class="btn-neon">Filter by Category</a>
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-top:30px; color:#e1e1ff;">How to Use</h2>
    <ul style="list-style:none; padding-left:0; margin-top:20px; line-height:1.8; color:#fff;">
        <li><strong>View Products:</strong> Head to <a href="/admin/products" class="btn-neon-outlined" style="padding:5px 10px; text-decoration:none;">Products Admin</a> to see all products, add new ones, or edit and delete existing items.</li>
        <li><strong>Manage Categories:</strong> Under <a href="/admin/categories" class="btn-neon-outlined" style="padding:5px 10px; text-decoration:none;">Categories Admin</a>, create or update categories to organize your products.</li>
        <li><strong>Manage Suppliers:</strong> Keep track of all suppliers and their details at <a href="/admin/suppliers" class="btn-neon-outlined" style="padding:5px 10px; text-decoration:none;">Suppliers Admin</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Filter by Category:</strong> Visit <a href="/filterbycategory" class="btn-neon-outlined" style="padding:5px 10px; text-decoration:none;">Filter by Category</a> to view products grouped by supplier without touching the URL bar.</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin-top:30px; line-height:1.6;">
        With Monster-Stop, we demonstrate a fully functional, stylish, and dynamic Blazor application integrated 
        with Entity Framework Core. Enjoy browsing, organizing, and managing your inventory like never before!
    </p>
</div>
